"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"中心化交易所（CEX）仍然是目前币圈不可或缺的\\n\\n1. 正规出入金唯一选择\\n2. 跨链减少损耗（A链a币充值到币安后出售再购买B链b币，提币到B链）\\n3. 安全存储加密资产（大型CEX比自己钱包要安全的多的多）\\n\\n币安是国内目前最大的中心化交易所，属于后来居上型，早已完成出海，一直比较坚挺。**不用挂梯子就能上**，操作界面比较友好（我心中操作体验最佳仍是火币）。实名认证(KYC)容易。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/L2_O2d7_Z3W2y3eVz04pJ.jpg?height=200&width=138)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1635849976,\"title\":\"CEX介绍及推荐\"},\"digest\":\"I78zQUmsI4LrwvsfotxJi1lFjeaSn7oUX9qgGj1duEQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x23af24b6601776849bBB2409a6Db6b17F51f2c28\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2uzowIqRSXrN6uxn8Ako6pGCVRhA5jPaz7oNOZCyGbI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"KKe4dewuJiBT99twK1jETQB_TdLyRUw_u2aXjYx0SkY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"4QpAu636MCpVOI5FwvSp4l98K8Tik-nDttZJ-ouQl4BWKALDZCSfUw658yutcUJ0p55kH7XtrjUxPxm-aELgVA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xe082cb4665c48a9bf1980df9ced3f120aed3a27a8942143462a8c84ea0669ced2128b1045cfa2e39d7c0fe73311b7989b96851995fe7c430373978db1499e3591c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2uzowIqRSXrN6uxn8Ako6pGCVRhA5jPaz7oNOZCyGbI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"KKe4dewuJiBT99twK1jETQB_TdLyRUw_u2aXjYx0SkY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"zWHwlaXjFPIPeKlJOzwWkWm9cbnP7prUFTOo6iI4h0Y\"}"